  <section class="about-us">
    <div class="container">
      <p>Codio is the cloud coding and content platform for teaching computer science in schools, universities and the vocational education sector.</p>

      <p>Education systems around the world are changing – at its heart, Codio is embracing this change as an education technology company pioneering support for teachers with a disruptive and innovative approach to help teach the world to code.</p>

      <p>Putting the needs of teachers first, and with a relentless focus on the student learning experience - Codio has been built by computer scientists, and specialists in user engagement, following extensive consultation with teachers and lecturers in computer science.</p>

      <p>Created originally to take the pain out of teaching computer programming, Codio uniquely combines a browser-based integrated development environment and coding platform with course content developed with student engagement and interaction in mind.</p>

      <p>By embracing the ideas that students and teachers are individuals, teaching styles differ and students advance at their own pace, Codio enables teachers and lecturers to support and coach students to better outcomes.</p>

      <p>Beyond responding to the renewed energy and focus in education systems globally on computing as the 4th science, Codio plans to tackle new approaches to other subjects in the future.</p>

